================================================================================
                  CDSA BLUE TEAM AGENT - START HERE
================================================================================

Welcome! You now have a complete blue team incident response system with
AI-powered forensic analysis. No API key needed!

================================================================================
                        CLAUDE CODE MODE (RECOMMENDED)
================================================================================

The easiest way to use this system:

1. Open in Claude Code:
   /home/stanner/blue_team_agent.py

2. Claude Code will automatically provide access to:
   - All forensic tools (ERIC Suite, Yara, Chainsaw)
   - MCP integration with your system
   - Real-time analysis and guidance

3. Ask me anything about Windows forensics:
   - "Analyze this event log for suspicious activity"
   - "Help me investigate a ransomware attack"
   - "Show me the timeline of what happened"

That's it! No setup, no API keys, just start investigating.

================================================================================
                       STANDALONE MODE (OPTIONAL)
================================================================================

If you want to run standalone without Claude Code:

1. Set your API key:
   export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="your-api-key"

2. Run the agent:
   bash quick_start.sh
   python3 blue_team_agent.py

3. Use interactively or with scenarios

