================================================================================
                        WHAT THIS SYSTEM DOES
================================================================================

‚úÖ Analyze Windows Forensic Artifacts
   - Event logs (EvtxECmd)
   - Registry hives (RECmd)
   - NTFS filesystems (MFTECmd)
   - Program execution (PECmd)
   - User activity (Jump Lists, Shortcuts, ShellBags)

‚úÖ Detect Malware & Threats
   - Scan with Yara signatures
   - Hunt with Chainsaw + Sigma rules
   - Identify malware families

‚úÖ Guide Investigations
   - AI-powered analysis and recommendations
   - Help reconstruct timelines
   - Correlate findings across artifacts
   - Document evidence professionally

‚úÖ Support CDSA Exam Preparation
   - Learn forensic concepts
   - Practice with realistic scenarios
   - Get feedback on analysis
   - Build investigation skills

================================================================================
                      REQUIRED CONFIGURATION
================================================================================

1. SET YOUR API KEY:
   export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="your-api-key-here"

   Get your API key from: https://console.anthropic.com

2. (OPTIONAL) SET ERIC TOOLS PATH:
   export ERIC_TOOLS_PATH="/path/to/ERIC"

   Default: /opt/ERIC

That's it! The system is configured.

================================================================================
                         AVAILABLE TOOLS
================================================================================

FORENSIC TOOLS:                  THREAT TOOLS:
‚úì EvtxECmd   - Event logs       ‚úì Yara       - Malware scanning
‚úì RECmd      - Registry         ‚úì Chainsaw   - Threat hunting
‚úì MFTECmd    - NTFS timeline
‚úì PECmd      - Program execution
‚úì JLECmd     - Recent files
‚úì LECmd      - Shortcuts
‚úì SBECmd     - Folder access

================================================================================
                        COMMON SCENARIOS
================================================================================

RANSOMWARE ATTACK?
‚Üí Type: "Help me investigate a ransomware attack"
‚Üí Analyze: Event logs, Prefetch, MFT
‚Üí Find: When it started, what encrypted files

LATERAL MOVEMENT?
‚Üí Type: "Check for lateral movement on this system"
‚Üí Analyze: Event logs (4624, 4625), Registry, Prefetch
‚Üí Find: Remote logons, credential use, pivot points

DATA EXFILTRATION?
‚Üí Type: "Investigate potential data exfiltration"
‚Üí Analyze: Jump Lists, ShellBags, MFT
‚Üí Find: What files accessed, when, by whom

MALWARE INFECTION?
‚Üí Type: "Scan for malware and persistence"
‚Üí Analyze: Yara scan, Registry, Prefetch
‚Üí Find: Malware family, persistence mechanisms

INSIDER THREAT?
‚Üí Type: "Analyze user activity for suspicious access"
‚Üí Analyze: Jump Lists, ShellBags, Event logs
‚Üí Find: What accessed, timeline, intent

